  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      Describe and analyze routes and modes of care for patients in emergency consultant in various
      emergency care and public psychiatric outpatient devices to provide useful information to
      optimize trajectories taken into psychiatric load on the Eurométropole territory upstream and
      downstream of where they viewed urgently.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
